---
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'BUPA Global in Australia', level: 2 },
  { id: 'coverage', text: 'Coverage Details', level: 2 },
  { id: 'bupa-australia', text: 'BUPA Global vs BUPA Australia', level: 2 },
  { id: 'plans-and-pricing', text: 'Plans and Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-its-for', text: 'Who Should Choose BUPA', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Health Insurance in Australia', href: '/countries/australia/insurance' },
  { title: 'BUPA Global Review', href: '/providers/bupa-global' },
  { title: 'BUPA vs Cigna', href: '/compare/cigna-global-vs-bupa-global' },
];

const planColumns = [
  { key: 'plan', header: 'Plan' },
  { key: 'coverage', header: 'Coverage' },
  { key: 'ausPrice', header: 'Australia (Age 35)' },
];

const planRows = [
  { plan: 'Essentials', coverage: 'Inpatient only', ausPrice: '$160-200/mo' },
  { plan: 'Comprehensive', coverage: 'Inpatient + Outpatient', ausPrice: '$250-320/mo' },
  { plan: 'Elite', coverage: 'Full coverage + extras', ausPrice: '$320-420/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="BUPA Global Health Insurance in Australia"
  description="Guide to using BUPA Global in Australia. UK-based international coverage with strong brand presence in Australia."
  headline="BUPA Global Health Insurance in Australia"
  subheadline="UK-based international coverage with strong Australian connections. Popular with British expats and families."
  heroBackgroundImage="/images/countries/australia-hero-bg.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get a BUPA Australia Quote"
  ctaButtonHref="/providers/bupa-global"
>
  <h2 id="overview">BUPA Global in Australia</h2>
  <p>
    BUPA Global is particularly well-positioned for Australia, given BUPA's significant local presence. While BUPA Global (international) and BUPA Australia (domestic) are separate products, the brand's Australian roots mean strong hospital relationships and local expertise.
  </p>
  <p>
    For UK expats especially, BUPA Global offers brand familiarity and coverage continuity. The plan provides premium international coverage that meets Australian visa requirements while remaining portable if you relocate.
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">Strong</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Local presence</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">Premium</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Service level</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">UK Expat</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Favorite</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Get a BUPA Global Quote"
    description="Premium international coverage with Australian expertise."
    buttonText="Get Quote"
    buttonHref="/providers/bupa-global"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="coverage">Coverage Details</h2>
  <p>
    BUPA Global plans include:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Inpatient care:</strong> Private hospital rooms, surgery, specialist treatment</li>
    <li><strong>Outpatient care:</strong> GPs, specialists, diagnostics (Comprehensive+)</li>
    <li><strong>Mental health:</strong> Strong coverage across plans</li>
    <li><strong>Maternity:</strong> Covered after 12-month waiting period</li>
    <li><strong>Cancer care:</strong> Comprehensive treatment coverage</li>
    <li><strong>Wellness:</strong> Health checks and screenings</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>BUPA's Australian Advantage</h3>
  <p>
    BUPA's Australian connections benefit Global members:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Strong relationships with major hospital groups</li>
    <li>Local claims processing capability</li>
    <li>Understanding of Australian healthcare system</li>
    <li>Potential coordination with BUPA Australia if transitioning</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="bupa-australia">BUPA Global vs BUPA Australia</h2>
  <p>
    These are different products for different situations:
  </p>

  <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-3">Key Differences</h3>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-blue-800">
      <li><strong>BUPA Global:</strong> International coverage, portable worldwide, suits expats who may relocate</li>
      <li><strong>BUPA Australia:</strong> Domestic private health insurance, meets Medicare Levy Surcharge requirements, only covers Australia</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p>
    For expats planning to stay in Australia long-term and eventually gain permanent residency, BUPA Australia may eventually make more sense. For those who might relocate or want international coverage, BUPA Global is the better choice.
  </p>

  <h2 id="plans-and-pricing">Plans and Pricing</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={planColumns} rows={planRows} />
  </div>

  <h3>Pricing Position</h3>
  <p>
    BUPA Global sits in the premium tier, typically priced similarly to Cigna Global. Expect to pay $200-400/month depending on plan tier and coverage options. The pricing reflects the premium service level and comprehensive coverage.
  </p>

  <h2 id="who-its-for">Who Should Choose BUPA in Australia</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-900 mb-3">Good Fit</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-green-800">
        <li>UK expats (brand familiarity)</li>
        <li>Families seeking premium coverage</li>
        <li>Those valuing mental health coverage</li>
        <li>Expats who may relocate within Asia-Pacific</li>
        <li>Corporate assignees</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Consider Alternatives</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Budget-conscious (Allianz, AXA)</li>
        <li>Short-term nomads (SafetyWing)</li>
        <li>Those seeking lowest price</li>
        <li>Students (need OSHC)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Ready for BUPA Global?"
    description="Get a personalized quote for Australia."
    buttonText="Get Your Quote"
    buttonHref="/providers/bupa-global"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Prices are estimates. BUPA Global and BUPA Australia are separate products. Verify coverage details directly with BUPA.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
